headline: Veteran Corporate Communications, Government Relations and Marketing Executives Form CorpBridge Advisors
summary: Drawing on decades of leadership at some of the world's most prominent companies in finance, technology, and media, senior executives have launched CorpBridge Advisors (www.corpbridgeadvisors.com), a firm specializing in corporate reputation, financial transactions, geopolitical issues and cross-border market entry into the U.S.
